Subject: Intro to Zenoss
Description: An Introduction to Network Monitoring utilizing the Zenoss Monitoring System. Topics covered will include configuration, managing monitored hosts, SNMP, SSH, and basic remediation.  Speakers include:Andrew Kirsch - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
